-- Marsh & McLennan Names McGlarry as General Counsel of Wyman Unit
-- B y   S t e v e n   N o r t o n
-- 2012-06-26T14:55:02Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-06-26/marsh-mclennan-names-mcglarry-as-general-counsel-of-wyman-unit.html
Marsh & McLennan Cos., the second-
largest insurance broker, named Paula McGlarry as general
counsel of the Oliver Wyman consulting subsidiary.  McGlarry, who joined the company in 2003, will report to
Marsh & McLennan General Counsel Peter J. Beshar and Wyman Chief
Executive Officer John Drzik, the New York-based company said
today in a statement distributed by Business Wire.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Steven Norton in  New York  at 
 Snorton7@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Dan Kraut at 
 dkraut2@bloomberg.net  